To work on the sources, without installing:
./configure --enable-maintainer-mode --enable-debug
(and $make all check)

To work on the sources, with local installation
./configure --enable-maintainer-mode --enable-debug --prefix=$HOME
(and $make all check install)

To do an optimized computation, with local installation
./configure --prefix=$HOME

To do an optimized computation, with root install:

./configure
make all check
sudo make install



